02:15.670 --> 02:16.220
Awak teruskan.

02:16.480 --> 02:17.370
Saya akan menyelamatkan Lifei.

02:17.670 --> 02:18.250
Awak...

02:21.670 --> 02:22.220
Baiklah.

02:22.550 --> 02:23.780
Zhaomin, berhati-hati.

02:24.040 --> 02:24.940
Jangan tarik perhatian.

02:24.960 --> 02:25.900
