02:25.990 --> 02:26.460
Faham.

02:27.760 --> 02:28.340
Zhaomin.

02:29.800 --> 02:30.370
Apa itu?

02:33.590 --> 02:34.500
Kita akan berbincang kemudian.

02:34.520 --> 02:35.180
Pergi selamatkan mereka.

02:47.920 --> 02:48.650
